{"tid":613770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【批鬥戴耀廷】人民日報續發功 梁美芬跟隊形斥誤導港獨是選項","createTime":"2018-04-02T03:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T03:54:34.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7be47ccc572ad9d1d06a2e23d25c5cd78924e017","tid":613770,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180402/large/1522636842_c880.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180402%2Flarge%2F1522636842_c880.jpg&h=225e4819&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佔中發起人、港大副教授戴耀廷早前到台灣參加論壇，提到香港可考慮成為獨立國家或聯邦後，先後被港澳辦和中聯辦點名炮轟提倡港獨，建制派全線狙擊，41名建制派立法會議員聯署譴責，並促戴向公眾認錯。經民聯梁美芬今早在電台節目「跟隊形」批評，聲言戴的發言違反基本法及中國憲法，觸碰法律及政治底線，誤導部分公眾認為港獨是香港選項之一。<br />\n<br />\n內地官方《人民日報》海外版刊登署名文章，接力批戴耀廷公開尋求境外支持企圖分裂國家，嚴重違反國家憲法、香港基本法和本港《刑事罪行條例》中的煽動條例，直接挑戰一國兩制底線，又指香港雖並無以港獨入刑的先例，但不等於法律規章無法處置港獨，特區政府不應再姑息縱容，要盡快追究以彰顯法治。<br />\n戴昨形容文革式批鬥已從他身上開始，很快會擴散至香港所有人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180402/58024196\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180402%2F58024196&d=hk8iL1Q5AFeEi9VmpvWFngCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=62bc8eab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180402%2F58024196&h=6c4b1735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180402/58024196</a>"},{"pid":"9ac716285790748bd09b3462ccb9b283a9eb497b","tid":613770,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:39:12.000Z","msg":"哎呀<br />\n又係保皇黨<br />\n中資股支持者保皇狗打手關愛座hunter又要準備拎泛民出來轉移視線"},{"pid":"a415a6761ad96f58ba1ebb1ff871c708e358eb2e","tid":613770,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:54:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}